Introduction

Daniela Avanzini is a Cuban/Venezuelan-American dancer, singer, and rapper under Geffen Records and HYBE Labels. She is best known as a member of the global girl group KATSEYE.

Daniela is recognized for her participation in the survival show "The Debut: Dream Academy", where she ranked 3rd and qualified for debut, becoming a member of the girl group KATSEYE.

On August 16, 2024, Daniela officially debuted as a member of KATSEYE with their first EP "SIS (SOFT IS STRONG)".

Prior to this, she participated in America’s Got Talent Season 8, SuperKids Europe, and So You Think You Can Dance.
